    @CreoleResource(name="MuNPEx French (FR) NP Chunker",
                comment="Multi-lingual Noun Phrase Extractor (MuNPEx) -- French",
                helpURL="http://www.semanticsoftware.info/munpex/",
                icon="jape")
public class MuNPExFRTransducer
extends gate.creole.Transducer
    The transducer for the Multi-lingual Noun Phrase Extractor (MuNPEx) configuration for French (FR) This is a JAPE transducer and this class is here to allow the specification in creole.xml of a default grammar to be used in MuNPEx.
